## Project Description
This is a personal portfolio website showcasing my skills, projects, and providing a way for visitors to contact me. The website is built with HTML5 and CSS, featuring a responsive design that works across all devices.

## Features
- Semantic HTML5 structure
- Responsive design (Desktop, Tablet, Mobile)
- Modern CSS with Flexbox and Grid
- Interactive elements and smooth transitions
- Portfolio showcase
- Contact form

## Project Structure
```
/
├── index.html          # Main page
├── about.html
├── contact.html
├── styles/
│   └── styles.css      # Main stylesheet
├── images/            # Image assets
└── README.md          # Project documentation
```

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone this repository
2. Open `index.html` in your web browser
3. No additional setup required --- this is a static website!

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS (Flexbox & Grid)
- Google Fonts
- Custom animations and transitions

## Responsive Design
The website is fully responsive with breakpoints at:
- Desktop: 1024px and above
- Tablet: 768px to 1023px
- Mobile: 480px and below 